PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 1997-323 that increases, from $5 billion CDN to $17 billion CDN, the amount thereby authorized to be raised on European financial markets by way of the issue and sale of Treasury Bills or Treasury Notes, and re-appoints the London Branch of the Royal Bank of Canada as registrar and fiscal agent.
Attachments
precis:
Amendment to Order in Council P.C. 1997-323 that increases, from $5 billion
CDN to $17 billion CDN, the amount thereby authorized to be raised on
European financial markets by way of the issue and sale of Treasury Bills
or Treasury Notes, and re-appoints the London Branch of the Royal Bank of
Canada as registrar and fiscal agent.
